&lt;p&gt;Are you registered physiotherapist who is looking for an interesting rotational post? We can offer what you are looking for. We offer rotations in , MSK outpatients, acute stroke , respiratory acute, medicine.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are looking for registered band 5 physiotherapists who are keen to work in an innovative way within the Community and Therapy service. You will be encouraged to build on the knowledge you gain in clinical areas, with encouragement to work differently; to follow patient pathway and be part of developing a flexible patient-centred service.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;What we ask in return? Committed, enthusiastic, team player who is willing to learn and have the ambition to be the best they can be.&lt;/p&gt;
